    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Hi, my mom got this recipe from a Palestinian friend of hers.  It was  a bit different:  lentils only, a big scoop of sour cream or yogurt, then an enourmous pile of deeply caramelized onions on top, with a big pour of good olive oil and a sprinkle of sea salt.  This was a favorite comfort food when I moved out on my own.  So much tastier than it seems!</p>
    </div>

